      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies with a crisp 8,000 RPM redline. The valvetrain has been shimmed to factory specifications, and the dual-VANOS system is fully overhauled to ensure precise cam phasing. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a ZF 6-speed manual gearbox and a GKN variable M-differential. Crucially, the chassis has undergone proactive subframe reinforcement, maintaining original torsional rigidity. Finished in Carbon Black with a pristine Nappa interior, this specimen retains its factory-correct staggered Style 67 alloys and original suspension geometry. A turn-key investment for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
